{"tid":2184671,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Biden競選團隊造勢新招 : 走入動森!!","createTime":"2020-09-01T17:11:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-01T18:50:13.000Z","uid":270889,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"8198421c46ab0c7ab940b867498979ebc6091230","tid":2184671,"uid":270889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T17:11:50.000Z","msg":"Biden又贏 !!! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n識得用奇招接觸年青選民 等佢地可以網上造勢 <br />\n新招一出網民反應亦都唔錯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/kellymakena/status/1300803269997006848?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkellymakena%2Fstatus%2F1300803269997006848%3Fs%3D20&d=H6IDb39AroI58YjM1eqeYWmu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=7c775e5f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkellymakena%2Fstatus%2F1300803269997006848%3Fs%3D20&h=84416356\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/kellymakena/status/1300803269997006848?s=20</a><br />\n網上造勢仲陸續有黎  侵應該輸到仆街了  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/kellymakena/status/1300803269997006848?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkellymakena%2Fstatus%2F1300803269997006848%3Fs%3D20&d=H6IDb39AroI58YjM1eqeYWmu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=7c775e5f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkellymakena%2Fstatus%2F1300803269997006848%3Fs%3D20&h=84416356\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/kellymakena/status/1300803269997006848?s=20</a><br />\n<br />\nStarting today, September 1st, Animal Crossing: New Horizons players will be able to deck out their island homes with official Joe Biden yard signs as part of the campaign&rsquo;s broader initiative to organize voters online this fall.<br />\n<br />\nSince the start of the coronavirus outbreak in the US earlier this year, campaigns like Biden&rsquo;s have been forced to entirely rethink how they organize voters. Instead of in-person rallies, Biden&rsquo;s team has opted for live-streamed events and fundraisers along with socially distanced productions and interviews. The entire Democratic National Convention was held virtually earlier this month, with most guests streaming in over video software like Zoom to deliver speeches.<br />\n<br />\nThe Biden-Harris campaign released four sign designs for players to download, featuring the official Biden-Harris logo, Team Joe logo, the &ldquo;Joe&rdquo; Pride logo, and an image of aviator sunglasses shaded in red, white, and blue. Players will be able to access the designs in-game by scanning the design QR codes through the Nintendo Switch Online app.<br />\n<br />\nAs part of the Biden-Harris campaign&rsquo;s plans to get the signs in front of voters, the team is seeding the designs with a handful of gaming influencers who will be sharing their gameplay with the merch throughout the day on Tuesday.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;This is just the start of how we plan to engage players ahead of November as we&rsquo;re already looking forward to rolling out more digital swag, voter education tools, and organizing efforts on Animal Crossing and other platforms,&rdquo; Tom said.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nHillary 2016都識用Pokemon Go 搞gag 糟仔盡得真傳 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vwaiyjh1dGk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dvwaiyjh1dGk&d=H6IDb39AroI58YjM1eqeYWmu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=fb1473cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vwaiyjh1dGk</a>"},{"pid":"d347e6e608573659f935ab161a7c9e05c7255ebc","tid":2184671,"uid":270889,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T17:13:01.000Z","msg":"自膠 po咗條link兩次 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\